text:
{
  "prompt": "A concept image of a futuristic electric scooter based on a skateboard-style frame. It has a flat and wide deck, a centrally mounted powerful mid-drive motor, and a low center of gravity. The front wheel is 20 inches with an aerodynamic cover, and the rear wheel is 18 inches wide and thick for stability. The suspension includes dual rear shocks and an upside-down front fork for superior comfort. The battery pack is integrated into the flat deck, resembling a skateboard. The handlebars are upright, with a digital display. The rear includes a cargo rack integrated into the seat design. The color scheme is a bold mix of matte black and orange, with a clean, high-tech urban aesthetic. The overall shape is streamlined, designed to rival a PCX125 in performance and style.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital rendering of a modern electric scooter with a bold design. The scooter has a sleek red and white color scheme. The front wheel is visibly larger (around 20 inches) than the rear, giving it an aggressive, performance-oriented look. It features a tall, adjustable windscreen, dual rear suspension, a comfortable black seat with a passenger backrest, and a robust rear rack for cargo. The frame is step-through, with a skateboard-style flat deck integrated with a battery pack. The scooter's branding reads '춘봉' in bold black lettering on the lower side panel. Set against a clean white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-quality digital rendering of a modern electric scooter designed with a sleek white and red color scheme. The scooter features an enlarged front wheel (visibly larger than the rear wheel), a flat skateboard-style deck, black saddle seat with backrest, red rear suspension, and alloy wheels. The handlebars are chrome, with a round headlight and a black front basket. The design is sporty yet practical, ideal for urban deliveries, and is set against a clean white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric scooter designed for urban delivery, featuring a sleek aerodynamic white and red body. The front fairing (cowl) is curved and extended, with an integrated clear windscreen and smooth lines. The seat is slim, sculpted for rider comfort, with lumbar support and integrated with a flat rear cargo platform. The frame is a skate-board style step-through design, with a large front wheel for stability and a smaller wide rear wheel. Twin rear suspension, metallic finish parts, and elegant branding complete the premium design. Displayed side-on against a clean white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic and aerodynamic electric scooter in a white and red color scheme, designed with a sleek curved front cowl extending over the front wheel, integrated aerodynamic windshield, and a slim, sporty seat with lumbar support. The rear seat is integrated into a flat cargo platform, all presented in a minimalistic studio background. The scooter features upgraded suspension, alloy wheels, and a clean, professional design ideal for urban delivery and long-range comfort.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
